  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if pre-operative vitamin D supplementation lowers
      the incidence of post-operative transient or permanent hypoparathyroidism in patients
      undergoing total thyroidectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
